reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on December 4, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Not what you think!
reviews.reviewText: I was worried and thought it was going to be cheap and would eventually not work(like the ones you buy from Marshall’s or Walgreens) but I’ve had these a couple months now and they still work great! Looks just like the apple charger. I always lose my charger and always have a low battery phone. This pack was amazing- an incredibly low price for 4 cords! I now have them on my night stand, in my car, husband truck, and kitchen! So nice to have a charger in different areas of the house so I don’t have to keep moving one around the house!! Definitely get yourself a pack!!!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on October 13, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 4.0 out of 5 stars Don’t stay connected
reviews.reviewText: These things have one job—to stick in the phone and charge it. Pretty simple. This doesn’t seem to hold the connection for longer than a few seconds, so it doesn’t charge when it should be. Waste of money. Durability and sturdiness don’t matter much if they don’t charge the device.UPDATE—These are fine. It turned out it was my phone port. Evidently, dust and lint gets in there and that interferes with the connection of the chargers and such. Changed my review to 4 stars.
